  "title": "M&E Manager",
  "description": "<p>Job Description:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Planning, programming and monitoring the processes of M&amp;E works and provide specific program</li>\n  <li>Responsible for carrying out M&amp;E technical meetings and resolving technical issues with record</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with client's representatives, consultants, and subcontractors on all technical matters</li>\n  <li>Monitor job progress and ensure that M&amp;E contracted works meet all requirements, quality and target completions</li>\n  <li>Appraisal for works and products compliance to specifications and requirements</li>\n  <li>Develop the details of Testing and Commissioning activities including Factory Tests, Individual System Test, Integrated System Test, RI, etc.</li>\n  <li>Responsible for variation order cost collection, cost verification of the VO works and make necessary recommendation of VO prices</li>\n  <li>To check, evaluate and confirm the work done and material supply quantity status for the purpose of M&amp;E subcontractor/NSC progress payments including instruction of progress substantiation documents from vendors</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum Diploma in Mechanical or Electrical Engineering </li>\n  <li>At least 10 years of M&amp;E experience in local construction industry and managed complex construction projects such as residential and commercial buildings</li>\n  <li>Demonstrates strong technical competence and excellent time management skills</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Knowledge/Skills/Abilities:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Strong technical knowledge in mechanical and electrical trades</li>\n  <li>Strong M&amp;E works installation knowledge with the ability to provide practical solution related with site installation</li>\n  <li>Good knowledge of Local Code/Regulation pertaining to M&amp;E services, building construction and safety</li>\n  <li>Strong time management skills with exceptional attention to detail and ability to manage particular tasks put in his charge</li>\n  <li>Good verbal and written communication skills</li>\n  <li>Ability to analyse and synthesize complex issues quickly and propose counter measures to settle the issues</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Suitable candidates are encouraged to apply this position via Apply Now button or email to Career@kah.com.sg</strong></p>\n<p><em>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</em></p>",
